Template: simple-motd/user
Type: string
_Description: Simple-MOTD User:
 If you want Simple-MOTD to display to a single user, enter the user
 name below.
 .
 To display Simple-MOTD to all users (including root), either leave blank or 
 input "all" below.
 .
 If a non-valid username is chosen, then it will default to be displayed to
 all users.
 .
 To change after installation one can run the following command again.
 .
 $ dpkg-reconfigure simple-motd
 .
